modules.description: This module implements Tar file manipulation using Eio, providing functions to extract, create, and fold over Tar archives with support for filtering and custom headers. It operates on Tar headers, extended headers, and source/sink flows or files, enabling precise control over archive structure and content. Concrete use cases include extracting filtered subsets of a Tar archive into a directory, creating Tar files from directory trees with specific compatibility levels, and appending individual files to a Tar stream with custom metadata.
